# Ben Naught 
Sat, May 24
| 
West Hills Vineyards
Come enjoy a night of authentic country music with Ben Naught live in our tasting room! His rich, heartfelt tunes and down-to-earth performance will have you tapping your feet and sipping on your favorite drinks. It’s the perfect evening for country music lovers—don’t miss it!
